10024
06:36:07.949 --> 06:36:08.909
Termómetro,

10025
06:36:09.069 --> 06:36:09.869
32

10026
06:36:09.869 --> 06:36:11.469
grados centígrados.

10027
06:36:11.949 --> 06:36:12.749
Hans,

10028
06:36:12.749 --> 06:36:13.789
