11862
07:49:20.343 --> 07:49:20.983
porque,

11863
07:49:21.223 --> 07:49:23.863
por grandes que sean las maravillas de la

11864
07:49:23.863 --> 07:49:24.743
naturaleza,

11865
07:49:25.063 --> 07:49:28.183
